{"tid":1719811,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實唔好再俾元朗鄉黑為所欲為","createTime":"2019-11-14T07:34:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T08:29:55.000Z","uid":35382,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"810a4b9fbe1a3e7d972660fbe6b3ba5fb4979898","tid":1719811,"uid":35382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:34:01.000Z","msg":"大家都知手足係荃灣二玻坊有手足俾人斬到殘癈<br />\n但大家記唔記得最令人震驚既<br />\n係721元朗鄉黑打人事件<br />\n自從個件事發生後 <br />\n除左一開頭試過村外圍堵及發現葉虎事件外<br />\n對班鄉黑根本冇阻嚇力<br />\n因為冇實際攪過佢地<br />\n荃灣我地點做？打到佢地怕 燒到佢地怕<br />\n呢幾個月黎 我地由和理非 遊行 <br />\n到一開始有手足拎住石頭俾人話暴力<br />\n到掉火魔法 又俾人話暴力<br />\n到而家手足做埋投石器<br />\n有邊一次唔係俾人話暴力？<br />\n所以根本就已經唔需要怕<br />\n有邊次我地係唔克制<br />\n但俾人打 俾人斬之後 我地有冇對付過佢地？<br />\n冇呀,冇攪過元朗班冚家剷呀 <br />\n所以,大家應該一齊<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">打柒鄉黑,燒佢條村</span></span>"},{"pid":"a239e4db3281c40432ab79b89f520a0c21deb075","tid":1719811,"uid":35382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:34:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1a26895c9dd9e32823e0f734188bafd2a50ff1af","tid":1719811,"uid":35382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:35:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"702b8d732ee25ecc07a64909930986b2e3a2a998","tid":1719811,"uid":35382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:35:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b43ddbd95c4ea788a2dc3ce527139f8320e94435","tid":1719811,"uid":35382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:35:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f270cb5f6e26364d4cbaf6128193191c5f4e024","tid":1719811,"uid":37959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:35:43.000Z","msg":"黑社會唔殺 光復左香港 香港人都唔會有安寧日子"},{"pid":"69a03338ec4529d5ca42dfc0ba24490f413ae24d","tid":1719811,"uid":35382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:36:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dfdc17bf96a09a14d35443b5ea0b01dbd413d882","tid":1719811,"uid":35382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":